about.summary: A Python port of the YUI CSS compression algorithm.

name: cssmin
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "cssmin" %}
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  sha256: 0649244b431c8d604d443047c66156cf5b0d0677c6beacbdaf40594ee2fd4ea4
  url: https://github.com/zacharyvoase/cssmin/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz

build:
  noarch: python
  script: python setup.py install  --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt
  number: 0
  entry_points:
    - cssmin = cssmin:main

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - cssmin
  commands:
    - cssmin --help

about:
  license_family: MIT
  license: MIT
  dev_url: http://github.com/zacharyvoase/cssmin
  doc_url: http://github.com/zacharyvoase/cssmin
  home: http://github.com/zacharyvoase/cssmin
  summary: A Python port of the YUI CSS compression algorithm.
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - csadorf
    - jenzopr
